Grammatik

    0 $accept: programm $end

    1 programm: object_list

    2 object_list: %empty
    3            | object_list object

    4 object: IDENTIFIER_PROC '{' object_list '}'
    5       | IDENTIFIER_PROC STRING ':' IDENTIFIER '{' object_list '}'
    6       | IDENTIFIER_PROC ':' IDENTIFIER '{' object_list '}'
    7       | IDENTIFIER_VAR STRING ';'
    8       | IDENTIFIER_VAR STRING ':' number_sum ';'
    9       | IDENTIFIER_VAR ':' number_sum ';'
   10       | IDENTIFIER_VAR STRING ':' string_sum ';'
   11       | IDENTIFIER_VAR ':' string_sum ';'
   12       | IDENTIFIER_VAR STRING ':' bool_or ';'
   13       | IDENTIFIER_VAR ':' bool_or ';'

   14 number_sum: number_sum '+' number_fac
   15           | number_sum '-' number_fac
   16           | number_fac

   17 number_fac: number_fac '*' number_term
   18           | number_fac '/' number_term
   19           | number_term

   20 number_term: NUMBER
   21            | '(' number_sum ')'

   22 string_sum: string_sum '+' string_term
   23           | string_term

   24 string_term: STRING
   25            | '(' string_sum ')'

   26 bool_or: bool_or IDENTIFIER_OR bool_and
   27        | bool_and

   28 bool_and: bool_and IDENTIFIER_AND bool_not
   29         | bool_not

   30 bool_not: '!' bool_not
   31         | bool_term

   32 bool_term: IDENTIFIER_TRUE
   33          | IDENTIFIER_FALSE
   34          | '(' bool_or ')'


Terminale und die Regeln, in denen sie verwendet werden

    $end (0) 0
    '!' (33) 30
    '(' (40) 21 25 34
    ')' (41) 21 25 34
